{"id":317705,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-湖北荆州镇长任拆迁总指挥实施野蛮强拆/","date":"2013-10-12T14:33:47Z","modified":"2013-10-12T14:33:47Z","title":"维权网 | 湖北荆州镇长任拆迁总指挥实施野蛮强拆（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）湖北省荆州市荆州区弥市镇政府实施野蛮暴力强拆，由镇长任拆迁总指挥，组织政府各职能部门工作人员参与实施强拆。没做任何补偿安置，没有任何合法手续，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">64</span><span>岁的张大妈因不同意拆迁，被从屋内野蛮暴力绑架出来，房屋被夷为平地，生活用品全部被砸在废墟中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>时许，家住弥市镇桥南新村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">46</span><span>号的张大妈家突然闯入一群人，不由分说将她从家里架出，塞进一辆白色面包车强行拖走。随后张大妈居住了近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>年的房子被挖掘机推倒，瞬间被夷为平地，家具和衣物等也一并被埋在瓦砾中。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据村民反映：此次强拆是由镇政府组织实施，是由镇长熊志波任拆迁总指挥的违法暴力强拆，主要事实和证据：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>一：拆迁方没有与被拆迁户达成协议。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>二：强拆程序违法，人民法院没有下达拆除通知书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>对于张大妈家此次遭遇的野蛮绑架强拆，镇政府领导给出的答案是：这是个误会，拆错了！　</span></div>\n<div><span>拆迁总指挥、镇长熊志波：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13972393447</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-VZhRogNYS1c/Ulk54nm4qAI/AAAAAAAApV8/8kM-TlIVD-w/s1600/158679642.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-VZhRogNYS1c/Ulk54nm4qAI/AAAAAAAApV8/8kM-TlIVD-w/s320/158679642.jpg\" width=\"254\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>被掩埋在废墟下的家具和衣物</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-pIFj2a85lT8/Ulk58_1W7rI/AAAAAAAApWE/ANRS3zpEM3w/s1600/158680023.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"217\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-pIFj2a85lT8/Ulk58_1W7rI/AAAAAAAApWE/ANRS3zpEM3w/s320/158680023.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}